sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Laptop User
    participant T as Desktop Tracker
    participant DB as Local SQLite
    participant Q as Sync Queue
    participant C as Convex Cloud
    participant W as Web Client

    U->>T: Work events, windows, tabs, files
    T->>DB: Persist raw capture + derived state
    T->>Q: Emit live delta / heartbeat
    Q->>C: Push live presence update
    C-->>W: Reactive freshness + current block update

    Note over T,Q: Near-live path target: seconds, not minutes

    T->>Q: Emit durable current-day delta
    Q->>C: Upload incremental work blocks / artifacts / entities
    C->>C: Materialize day summaries + search index
    C-->>W: Dashboard / history / search now reflect new state

    alt Laptop offline or cloud unreachable
        Q->>Q: Retain unsent deltas locally
        C-->>W: Mark workspace stale after threshold
    else Healthy path
        C-->>W: Show linked + fresh + synced
    end

    Note over DB,C: SQLite remains canonical, and cloud is the remote access layer
